comments: Orlando does not attempt a shot before the 24-second shot clock expires.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) collapses his arms as he absorbs the incoming contact from Wagner (ORL) during the screen.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) gathers the pass on his right foot and takes two steps before releasing the pass.
Wagner (ORL) gets drawn in the air and brushes Payton II's (GSW) body as he lands towards the floor, and the contact that occurs is marginal.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) slightly extends his arms into Isaac's (ORL) body as he establishes a screening position, which does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the pick.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) legally contests Banchero's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) briefly grasps Jackson-Davis' (GSW) jersey and releases as Jackson-Davis starts to roll towards the basket after the pick.
Banchero (ORL) contests the driving shot attempt and the contact that occurs with Curry's (GSW) arm after the release is marginal.
Wiggins (GSW) extends his hand into Wagner's (ORL) front at the start of the drive, which affects his SQBR.
Isaac (ORL) establishes himself in Thompson's (GSW) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Thompson (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Anthony (ORL) during the drive and absorbs the contact.
The ball is last touched by Anthony (ORL) prior to it going out of bounds.
Curry's (GSW) hand grazes Suggs' (ORL) body as he releases during his step-back. The contact is marginal.
Wagner (ORL) gathers the ball on his left foot and establishes his right foot as his pivot, which he maintains.
Wiggins (GSW) briefly places his forearm on Wagner's (ORL) body before aligning alongside his path at the beginning of the drive, which he can move through.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Wiggins (GSW) cleanly blocks Wagner's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) cleanly deflects the loose ball away from Wiggins (GSW) during the rebound before incidental contact occurs.
